name: Rose
description: Rose is a meme token on the BNB Smart Chain, inspired by a viral X post from Aster DEX on September 24, 2025, portraying Rose as Aster's "sister" through playful wordplay. With a 1,000,000,000 token supply, zero taxes, locked liquidity, and renounced ownership, it promotes decentralized community engagement. Rose serves as a speculative digital asset, traded on platforms like PancakeSwap, fostering meme culture and social interaction within the BNB ecosystem.
